To enable spamdyke, set:

qmailsmtpd_presmtpd="${PREFIX}/bin/spamdyke --config-file ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/spamdyke.conf"

in /etc/rc.conf, then restart qmail-smtpd.

===========================================================================
